\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 14, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nmp1665702736587.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nmp1665702736587.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nmp1665702736587.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nmp1665702736587\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"nmp1665702736587__sql_generation_messages_493078\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">If SQL generation fails, Uniface reports a warning or error.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For details, refer to the following information:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nmp1665702736587__li_d52994e1_d52995e1_d52996e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iur1665703279162.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iur1665703279162.html\" title=\"The DBMS connector, as specified by a database path, is unknown, or the DBMS client binaries are not available.\">Error: No SQL generated, DBMS driver DB not available.</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nmp1665702736587__li_d52997e1_d52998e1_d52999e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vdw1665703279302.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vdw1665703279302.html\" title=\"The descriptor for the specified entity is not available or not recognized.\">Error: No SQL generated for &lt;Entity.Model&gt;, Entity Descriptor not found.</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nmp1665702736587__li_d53000e1_d53001e1_d53002e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scb1665703279442.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scb1665703279442.html\" title=\"The SQL generation process takes path and entity redirection into account. No SQL is generated if a database path is directed to a different DBMS connector, or for entities that are redirected to a different DBMS connector.\">Warning: No SQL could be generated for &lt;Entity.Model&gt;, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path &lt;$Path&gt; to a different DBMS driver</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nmp1665702736587__li_d53003e1_d53004e1_d53005e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ehl1665703279524.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ehl1665703279524.html\" title=\"The DBMS connector, as specified by a database path, is unknown on the server, the DBMS client binaries are not available, or the DBMS connector is redirected to a different DBMS connector.\">Warning: No SQL could be generated for &lt;Entity.Model&gt;, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path &lt;$Path&gt; to TCP, and the remote installation failed to connect to the requested database driver.</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nmp1665702736587__li_d53006e1_d53007e1_d53008e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bmj1665703279605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bmj1665703279605.html\" title=\"A connector option specified for the target DBMS is not supported by /gensql. For example, if you specified USYS$ORA_params = upgrade packages, no create table scripts are generated.\">Error: No SQL generated, /genSql does not support driver option &lt;Option&gt; as specified in the assignment file, [DRIVER_SETTINGS], USYS$&lt;DB&gt;_PARAMS.</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530329\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530329\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SQL Generation Messages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 14, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 If SQL generation fails, Uniface reports a warning or error. For details, refer to the following information: Error: No SQL generated, DBMS driver DB not available. Error: No SQL generated for <Entity.Model>, Entity Descriptor not found. Warning: No SQL could be generated for <Entity.Model>, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path <$Path> to a different DBMS driver Warning: No SQL could be generated for <Entity.Model>, because the ASN file redirects the entity or the path <$Path> to TCP, and the remote installation failed to connect to the requested database driver. Error: No SQL generated, /genSql does not support driver option <Option> as specified in the assignment file, [DRIVER_SETTINGS], USYS$<DB>_PARAMS. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}